window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She’s twelve. He’s dead. But together they’re going to save the world. Hopefully.</p> <p> <strong>The iconic first book in the bestselling Skulduggery Pleasant series.</strong> </p> <p>Stephanie's uncle Gordon is a writer of horror fiction. But when he dies and leaves her his estate, Stephanie learns that while he may have written horror, it certainly wasn't fiction.</p> <p>Pursued by evil forces, Stephanie finds help from an unusual source – the wisecracking skeleton of a dead sorcerer…</p>"; 
